  "body": "<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n  <img alt=\"kofi-singular-alt\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular-alt_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/RenderTweaks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n  <img alt=\"codeberg\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/codeberg_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/render-tweaks\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"sinytra connector\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6j289t.svg\">\n</a>\n\n# Render Tweaks\n\nAllows modifying the rendering of some in world things.\n\nAll color options have full customizability, including chroma.\n\n## Features\n\n### Lightning Bolt\n\n- Disable Lightning Bolt\n- Lightning Bolt Color\n\n### Fishing Line\n\n- Disable Fishing Lines\n- Fishing Line Color\n\n### World Border \n\nFor all three stages, stationary, growing, and shrinking (individually customizable)\n- Disable World Border\n- World Border Color\n",
